IMPL_FINANCE_DECOUPLING.title: Module Implementation: Finance Decoupling (Wave 16)
IMPL_FINANCE_DECOUPLING.instruction_raw: Implement the decoupling of Finance module from ISimulationState as specified in MISSION_IMPACT_FINANCE_SPEC.md. Enforce Public DTO mapping and Protocol-based communication.

IMPL_GOVERNMENT_DECOUPLING.title: Module Implementation: Government Decoupling (Wave 16)
IMPL_GOVERNMENT_DECOUPLING.instruction_raw: Refactor Government module to use Public API and stateless indicators as specified in MISSION_IMPACT_GOVERNMENT_SPEC.md. Decouple GovernmentDecisionEngine from concrete brain classes.

IMPL_LIFECYCLE_DECOUPLING.title: Module Implementation: Lifecycle Decoupling (Wave 16)
IMPL_LIFECYCLE_DECOUPLING.instruction_raw: Refactor Lifecycle systems to use context-based protocols (ILifecycleContext) as specified in MISSION_IMPACT_LIFECYCLE_SPEC.md. Eliminate all direct SimulationState dependencies.
